data.description: Discover your perfect home in Mill Creek at Wilson's Mills. Built in 2022, this fresh and modern 2,011 sq ft Home features 4 Bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and a 2-car garage. Enjoy the practicality of a spacious, open-plan living area, a sleek kitchen with sink in island which is great for entertaining and a cozy .15-acre yard. Home backs up to Wilson's Mills Community Park. Small Community Feel. Great location with easy access to HWY70 & short commute to 2 shopping plazas at Flowers Plantation.
